name: This Space of Ours
description:
This Space of Ours

Some say it's a backroom, others say it’s a facility. I call it home. OUR home. Help me expand this space of ours and you’ll find the meaning of your existence.

CONTROLS

  • A and D to move.
  • W to Jump.
  • E to interact.

Done playing?
